Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库斯科工业区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距我们出生很久以前就是军需产业…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是陆战兵器的开发特别突出的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个库斯科工业区被木星蜥蜴占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还配备了以往在任何战线都没有使用过的新型武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁这个新型武器就是我们这次的任务吗？提督
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部称它为"竹节虫"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:31.65,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,0)\bord0\shad0\1c&HE0EFEF&\pos(307,380)\fscy160\fs59}若注意的话  『约定』?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前军方的特种部队前去破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三次都被全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不经济啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让抚子上场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用重力波炮解决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  用远距离射击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的策略吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从经济方面看  我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且AESTIVALIS也可以不必涉险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话不要绕圈子嘛  小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就直说是明人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻开始作战！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果认真一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会让机械怪兽逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我少说废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  健  快住手  丈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距作战开始时间八分三十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重力波炮连接能源辅助回路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源补充同时露出山头发射重力波炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距预定作战点  还有17000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  你的拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳头也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手言和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要言和当然只有握手了  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一般打架不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相转移引擎全系统没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁出力下降l3％
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终安全装置解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距预定作战点1500
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距预定作战点800
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里被打中了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害扩及十八区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相转移引擎停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"竹节虫"的真面目一定是重力波轨道炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法操舵  即将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将坠落！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助引擎全开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠强力的重力控制  制造微黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是听解说的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠重力控制加速射出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然威力惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为微黑洞的形成需要花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想暂时是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你宝贵的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在开始该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是得靠AESTIVALIS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对空攻击系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方的迎击部队全是被这个消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的位置也可能遭对方攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的事情你早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我没说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之AESTIVALIS从空中接近也是同样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考量经济因素的话还真是头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员可不只是伤脑筋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从空中也不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹节虫的微黑洞弹的生成要十二小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是十七点遭到的攻击所以下一次攻击是明早五点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  谢谢你宝贵的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再拖了  马上派出破坏部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说只好从陆地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  明白了  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS从陆地接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行破坏竹节虫的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时后开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:46.70,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}当天18点  驾驶员简报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以空战两架路战三架的编组出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战指挥由赤月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你担任了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要离开抚子行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法得到能量供给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此靠这个外部电瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由各路战用AESTIVALIS背着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望作战能够成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你们的合作就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真幸运  中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好信用卡没钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻署的怪兽  当然（同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为再怎么说  优秀的指挥官是胜利的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人要不要喝果汁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星苏打可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是靠指挥官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有指挥官是没办法打仗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事前的准备也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有日常的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  给你果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  怎么了啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了什么不该说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由伙伴天河明人来担任物资补给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是伙伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物资补给由明人负责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就尽量装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实没有什么伙伴不伙伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始十五分前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各驾驶员及机械士请进行最后检查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经切为独立频道  没有其他人会听见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你说几句话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的敌人有那样强大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影机的影像清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  明人机OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要安全归来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我这样说你会觉得我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果你平安回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的交往可以更进一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下  有特别通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百..百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经切为独立频道  没有其他人会听见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你说几句话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的敌人有那样强大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我好担心好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要安全归来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  谁能传特别通讯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我这样说你会觉得我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你平安回来的话我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往可以更进一步对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴  明人也是一样的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人不可以这样  请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷梅从刚才开始一直在叫你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便餐没什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我准备了很多食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也用不着这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流的厨师要能随时应付顾客的点菜这是铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  我们是伙伴伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能辜负女孩子的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真可恨  羡慕死了！天河明人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的cosplay吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢要我们这样穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这样比较有作战司令部的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是他个人的收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的作业也开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士正在分析观测卫星传来的最新资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会得到新的情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS队脱离能量线有效范围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白痴白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  难道你的不喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是大人了
