Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸长手臂  咻咻咻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起走过地雷原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:54.37,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,300)\1c&HE0EFEF&\bord0\be1}当天21点30分  莫亚那平原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起迈步走  飒飒飒飒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四  二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起围绕着营火来休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围个圈圈大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS是愉快的好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起歌唱  大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  饭还没好?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是中华锅适合大火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  四十五分钟之后出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉动作还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光也要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也有那边的青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦呼唤着明日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:12:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀地高呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什么事  凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  天河还是笨笨的老样子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊  突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只顾做菜  自己都还没吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  光看到你就心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别放在心上啊  混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴  这是你自己做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象青春连续剧的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要我说的话好像有点不健康
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要受他的影响太大喔  凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢动画等的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不善谈恋爱想要柏拉图式爱情会误了对方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象你这么好的女孩子陷入那种模式的话太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该要更爽快  开朗点的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你不善谈恋爱好像过分了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来舰长跟小惠都为你倾倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我修正前言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是看不起别人的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对这点要订正订正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不喜欢看什么动画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没碍到你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我还不是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌袭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上把敌人的影像传过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洗车子  那是战车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战车?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪你们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是两世代前的陆战主力兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  洋化点的说法就是AFV
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  想靠战车来守住地面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场调度  有效利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方也采取经济的战法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该学着点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月跟明人趁现在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是再怎么旧式的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量多了也能构成威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然资料不足  但情况很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多糟？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  非常糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪费弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个炮战模组是对付竹节虫的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给凉子她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电瓶被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶  可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  快住手  天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  满意了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹节虫启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于资料不足  无法确知微黑洞弹何时发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可以确定一件事  下次受创将更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的微黑洞是因飞出太空之后自然蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有最小程度受损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定会在大气中蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不会错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人可也不是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么会造成怎样的后果呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨胀的放射热在一瞬间将都市蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃过这一劫的地方也会被强烈的伽玛射线…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战模式从A转变为D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安来来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就伤脑筋了  我们可动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  电瓶已经全给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩笑开得太过火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量跟弹药都所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后不准擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好神气的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来跟之前的玩具不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTI配备有吸着地雷  快去拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  正在拿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光  地雷还没好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的AESTI…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战车底部的装甲是最薄弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以瞄准车身的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车身是指战车的车体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不是指船的船体喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻眼睛  命中(音同亲眼睛)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  诸位?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实地攻击弱点就算空手打倒也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急联络  赶快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要逃可是小AESTI动不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才状况变得有点危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在竹节虫周围的空间重力波的变动增大中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理来不及啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去要怎么向司令部报告…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督  非常谢谢您的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的舰长越是危急的时候就越是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她对成员有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样直接冲到竹节虫那去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗? 天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入苦战啦  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之大家是伙伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊  天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人负责去竹节虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们负责在这里阻止战车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么就是这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去收拾竹节虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去收拾战车！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓稳咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然… 阻止她也不会听的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大战车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样对付的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了  马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,165)}辅助电池所剩无几！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.09,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注意！弹药快完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候不浪费弹药的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说啦  不能浪费弹药嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:08.37,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,140)}可惜！辅助电池用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好干得好  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赤月  作战终了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够来接我们那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然出了不少差错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过辛苦了  天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蛮能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好下一本同人志的标题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用"男人的友情天地"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  要我帮忙办人气投票？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:50.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很久很久以前  思兼这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:55.39,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我是机械?还是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:22:00.58,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}宇宙漫画的决定版
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是凑小姐成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  小光的眼镜也实在不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是舰长的胸部漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还是"白痴白痴"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我投星野琉璃一票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此  下集  机动战舰是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚本首藤刚志所呈献的星野琉璃传奇三部曲第二弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那『忘不了的日子』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集大家也一起投票…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  大家一起看喔
